procster (0.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging.
  * Package the libproc2-based procster HTTP/JSON process service.
  * Include systemd service unit and default configuration file.
  * Document upstream usage, debugging, and deployment notes.
  * Carry current upstream support for process listing, process trees,
    process termination, and newer-distribution build targets.

